    {
      "_id": "jBhOIaf2pCoDTeaR",
      "name": "Steal Body",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Inteligência: CD 12, one Small or Medium creature within 1,5 m that fica com a condição Incapacitado, is a Humanoid or Beast, and has 10 Pontos de Vida or fewer. The intellect devourer possesses o alvo, consumes its brain, and teleports inside its skull. While there, the intellect devourer has Total Cover against attacks and other effects originating outside its host. The intellect devourer retains its Inteligência, Sabedoria, and Carisma scores; its understanding of Fala Profunda; its telepatia; and its Detect Inteligência trait. It otherwise adopts o alvo's game statistics. It knows everything o alvo knew, including spells and languages.\nIf the host body dies, the intellect devourer must leave it. The intellect devourer is also forced out if o alvo regains its devoured brain by means of a Wish spell. By spending 1,5 m of its movement, the intellect devourer can voluntarily leave the body, teleporting to the nearest unoccupied space within 1,5 m of it. The body then dies unless its brain is restored before the end of the intellect devourer's next turn.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
